This project is for those who love to play cricket. This application is going to take login credentials of the player then player is going to upload his/her availability. 
This application will require the user to pay a minimum fee for the purchase of equipments and Venue selection. 
The System also requires the age of player in order to divide them into groups according to their age groups.
System creates the teams and scheduler make schedules of the matches and venue.
System sends the final confirmation to the user for the decided matches and after user confirms then the user is scheduled for the match.
Players are rewarded who perform well.
Scores are also available by the system.
That's it!!
